  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, we intend to error-annotate the output of the LLMs according to annotation criteria for learner corpora in order to be able to compare the frequency of the generated error types with the frequency of the error type in learner corpora and use this information as an additional criterion for the plausibility of the errors and quality of the LLM output.",
    "Additionally, we plan to explore the effects of fine-tuning a large language model for this task specifically based on error-annotated learner corpora.",
    "The ILAP system is currently available at https://ilap.kibi.group.",
    "Proceedings of the 13th Workshop on Natural Language Processing for Computer Assisted Language Learning (NLP4CALL 2024)",
